			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well, I think a better answer is this:
<br />

<br />
In the folder &quot;templates&quot; there should be the folders &quot;Prosilver&quot;.
<br />

<br />
* The installation instructions (&quot;install.txt&quot;) describe how to change the file &quot;templates/subSilver/profile_add_body.tpl&quot;. Repeat the changes also for the file &quot;templates/Prosilver/profile_add_body.tpl&quot;.
<br />

<br />
* Also, copy the file &quot;templates/subSilver/admin/textual_confirmation.tpl&quot; to the file &quot;templates/Prosilver/admin/textual_confirmation.tpl&quot;.<br />_________________<br />Oleg Parashchenko, bbAntiSpam
